{"tid":1316604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣呼籲] 計我話，今晚之後連儂牆應該係文宣之牆，貼 \"昨晚TVB不會告訴你的事\"","createTime":"2019-07-14T16:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T15:13:36.000Z","uid":54684,"like":366,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":122,"replies":[{"pid":"f5adc30c2df6e8b81a3c995e6d59e03510d3048a","tid":1316604,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:21:33.000Z","msg":"咁耐以來，連儂牆都係主要貼打氣說話，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">計我話，浪費哂</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今晚之後，大家要好好利用佢！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今晚警方初入新城市廣場個陣，我係Cable度見到警察同記者有衝突，重似乎有人用警棍想打記者。打記者！？<br />\n之後，又有好多衝突畫面，大家手上都有唔少料嘞<br />\n依家商場重出聲明，澄清事件<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">TVB？對政府不利既消息，佢當然好多都無啦</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">得我地知  街外人唔知   唔得既！[red]</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n計我話，全部應該貼上連儂牆<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>&quot;早上好！你知道嗎？TVB不會告訴你的事！&quot;</strong><br />\n<strong>&quot;大家都報了，就是TVB絕不會告訴你的事！&quot;</strong><br />\n<strong>&quot;Cable/Now告訴你真相！&quot;</strong></span><br />\n<strong>附上各種真消息，真圖片畀廣大市民知道，今晚發生咩事</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><em>點解會係商場出事呢？係咪有人驅趕令商場受損？定係點？<br />\n係咪有人打記者？<br />\n係咪有人殘害市民手臂？<br />\n係咪有人有心想係商場出亂事，搞亂民居，連食個飯都唔得？</em></span><br />\n<strong>我估沉默既大多數市民都好想知，TVB係咪收埋左D野無講佢地知！</strong><br />\n<br />\n咁做有以下好處<br />\n(1) 打擊TVB公信力<br />\n(2) 增強Cable/Now/RTHK公信力<br />\n(3) 增強正義市民士氣，打擊壞人士氣<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[red]<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n今後重有唔少遊行示威，事態發展甚多，<br />\n建議文宣組好好利用cable/now/apple既報導<br />\n比對TVB既報導<br />\n好好用連儂牆<br />\n發揮bulletin board文宣作用<br />\n塊版唔係只係打下氣咁簡單架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"66da8e41044331b475be42069376d18dc15bfcc1","tid":1316604,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792bbce9a420f0f2ced2f37a9a8c02b861ffa580","tid":1316604,"uid":216253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:27:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eca6813fba6f1a2dfb591e7f257ddf2b878f6962","tid":1316604,"uid":184985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ad1be99eac8f9f9c81bde6bb5018673a9871fa2","tid":1316604,"uid":32675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"推到十八區連儂牆"},{"pid":"4849fd41e9d146cb6fa36f67ed81b2eb254affbf","tid":1316604,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e51d8130954884bed4fe28b4a0d50592552b26d","tid":1316604,"uid":54684,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:34:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/aaronmcn/status/1150402892613898242?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faaronmcn%2Fstatus%2F1150402892613898242%3Fs%3D21&d=LzMeHrLekQtOmJ7gjClTQHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=2979fbe0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faaronmcn%2Fstatus%2F1150402892613898242%3Fs%3D21&h=25c6a8f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/aaronmcn/status/1150402892613898242?s=21</a><br />\n警察持武器闖入沙田中心民居，大批居民十分氣憤，紛紛驅趕警察<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家說這個畫面是不是應該貼一下</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6df2fdca433d5aefb8b466d1d5c53df80d451e2d","tid":1316604,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0910aed8465842f91632543fdbf80379a3cddf","tid":1316604,"uid":133903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:39:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\